  <h2>The Discipline is:</h2>
  <p>an <span class="def" id="in-school-suspension">in-school suspension*</span>.</p>
</div>
  <h2>Response:</h2>
  <p>There  are no restrictions on in-school suspensions, provided that your child:</p>
  <ul>
  <li>is given services that allow him or her  to continue to appropriately progress in the general curriculum  </li>
  <li>continues to receive the services  specified on his or her <span class="def" id="504">504 Plan*</span>, and</li>
  <li>continues to participate with children  without disabilities to the extent he or she would have in his or her current  placement. For example, if your child was in the regular education classroom, he  or she must be assigned to the same in-school suspension room as children  without disabilities.</li>
  </ul>
